OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of arson
OL,4,Cafter fire at Golders Green memorial
OL,5,Cwall
OL,7,FTwo people have been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of arson over a fire at a
OL,9,Fmemorial wall in Golders Green, north
OL,10,FLondon, the Metropolitan Police said.
OL,12,FA 46-year-old man and a 38-year-old
OL,13,Fwoman were arrested on Monday morning
OL,14,Fand taken to a London police station,
OL,15,Fwhere they remain in custody.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
