PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777950276
OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of arson
OL,4,Cafter fire at Golders Green memorial
OL,5,Cwall
OL,7,FThe arrests are part of an ongoing
OL,8,FCounter Terrorism Policing (CTP)
OL,9,Finvestigation following a reported
OL,10,Farson attack on a memorial wall in
OL,11,FLimes Avenue at around 12.15 am on
OL,12,FApril 27.
OL,14,FThe wall contains pictures of
OL,15,Fprotesters who were allegedly killed
OL,16,Fby the Iranian state in January.
OL,18,FThe wall incident is one of a number
OL,19,Fof suspected antisemitic arson attacks
OL,20,Fin the area being investigated by
OL,21,Fpolice in recent weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
