PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777950276
OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of arson
OL,4,Cafter fire at Golders Green memorial
OL,5,Cwall
OL,7,FCommander Helen Flanagan, head of
OL,8,FCounter Terrorism Policing (CTP)
OL,9,FLondon, said in a statement: "We are
OL,10,Fcommitted to protecting vulnerable
OL,11,Fcommunities in the capital.
OL,13,F"Detectives have been conducting
OL,14,Fextensive enquiries since this
OL,15,Fincident was reported to us last week
OL,16,Fand these two arrests are the result
OL,17,Fof that hard work.
OL,26,@qD@^OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
