CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777950276
OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of arson
OL,4,Cafter fire at Golders Green memorial
OL,5,Cwall
OL,7,F"CTP London is working on a number of
OL,8,Finvestigations into incidents that
OL,9,Fhave taken place in north west London
OL,10,Fsince the attack on Hatzola ambulances
OL,11,Fin Golders Green in March.
OL,13,F"We have made a total of 30 arrests,
OL,14,Fand nine people have been charged.
OL,16,F"Counter-terrorism officers continue
OL,17,Fto work closely with our colleagues in
OL,18,Fthe Metropolitan Police in response to
OL,19,Fthe various incidents.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@AOU
