OL,7,F"We're providing protective security
OL,8,Fadvice and support to various
OL,9,Forganisations, community venues and
OL,10,Fbusinesses.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FShe added: "With the threat level now
OL,18,Fraised to severe, everyone can play
OL,19,Ftheir part to keep themselves and
OL,20,Ftheir communities safe.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@LOU
